---
title: Southeast Asian Beef & Creamy Coconut Sauce with Rapid Rice & Veggies
description: Make a simple beef stir-fry a little more special by cooking it in a mouth-watering coconut sauce. Complete with our Southeast
Asian spice blend lending a big hit of flavour (and with minimal effort), you’ll be pleasantly surprised by all that this colourful
creation has to offer!
